{"type": "article", "id": 27289, "title": "家用自行车", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-25T06:32:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 94, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162646KcqRZobDfsx6TL4t.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>想骑着自行车和孩子一起出行？你可能需要这辆家用自行车 Taga。它的设计灵感来自荷兰的货载自行车，它们通常在前面放置了一个可以盛放货物的木箱——而 Taga 搭载的是可以折叠并且自由组合的箱体，配套的组件有婴儿椅、扶手、遮阳篷甚至水枪，可以满足家庭出行的各种需要。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/taga2/taga-20-the-ultimate-most-affordable-family-bike\">链接</a>参与它的众筹，如果你不清楚该购买哪些配套组件，专用的<a href=\"https://tross.typeform.com/to/gihTEP\">导购页面</a>可以帮你完成个性化的定制。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162641MjzwTJeip3buGXUS.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162644kMaBqT6zLi92woSU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.92690058\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162644wPVp9gGlSO7Mzb8B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91285081\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162645oTqKZH7Gs21eM5n0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93083573\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}